{"analysis_path": "obsidian-vault/analysis/ICLR_2026/A.I.R._Enabling_Adaptive_Iterative_and_Reasoning-based_Frame_Selection_For_Video_Question_Answering.md", "core_operator": "查询与帧之间关系的语义理解深度和计算分配策略。通过VLM只对少量高潜帧进行推理分析，并利用局部密度采样迭代扩展相关区域，在控制计算成本的同时实现准确选择。", "datasets": ["Video-MME", "LongVideoBench", "NextQA"], "method_groups": ["Vision / Multimodal / 3D", "LLM / Reasoning / Alignment"], "methods": ["A.I.R."], "paper_link": "https://openreview.net/forum?id=SZVpOKw0YD", "pdf_ref": "obsidian-vault/paperPDFs/ICLR_2026/A.I.R._Enabling_Adaptive_Iterative_and_Reasoning-based_Frame_Selection_For_Video_Question_Answering.pdf", "primary_logic": "利用强大的VLM进行深度语义分析，但通过迭代循环仅处理少量高潜帧，并通过局部密度采样发现被轻量模型低估的关键帧，从而在计算效率上实现VLM分析的可处理性，同时保持高精度帧选择。", "project_link": "", "source": "analysis", "tags": ["topic/vision_multimodal_applications", "topic/vision_multimodal_applications/vision_models_multimodal"], "title": "A.I.R.: Enabling Adaptive, Iterative, and Reasoning-based Frame Selection For Video Question Answering", "topics": ["Vision / Multimodal / Applications"], "venue": "ICLR", "year": 2026}
{"analysis_path": "obsidian-vault/analysis/ICLR_2026/A2TG_Adaptive_Anisotropic_Textured_Gaussians_for_Efficient_3D_Scene_Representation.md", "core_operator": "基于梯度引导的自适应纹理控制策略：利用位置梯度筛选需要高频细节的高斯，再根据高斯两个轴的比例各向异性地上采样纹理分辨率与宽高比，从而实现按需分配纹理参数。", "datasets": ["DeepBlending", "Mip-NeRF360"], "method_groups": ["Vision / Multimodal / 3D", "Representation / Self-Supervised / Transfer"], "methods": ["A^2TG (Adaptive Anisotropic Textured Gaussians)"], "paper_link": "https://openreview.net/forum?id=EPN5MU4liR", "pdf_ref": "obsidian-vault/paperPDFs/ICLR_2026/A2TG_Adaptive_Anisotropic_Textured_Gaussians_for_Efficient_3D_Scene_Representation.pdf", "primary_logic": "通过梯度驱动的高斯筛选与各向异性上采样，纹理分辨率集中在场景高频、高可见区域，大量背景或低细节高斯保留1×1极小纹理，在保持渲染质量的同时显著降低内存开销，并避免均匀正方形纹理的冗余。", "project_link": "", "source": "analysis", "tags": ["topic/vision_multimodal_applications", "topic/vision_multimodal_applications/3d_rendering_reconstruction"], "title": "A^2TG: Adaptive Anisotropic Textured Gaussians for Efficient 3D Scene Representation", "topics": ["Vision / Multimodal / Applications"], "venue": "ICLR", "year": 2026}
{"analysis_path": "obsidian-vault/analysis/ICLR_2026/3DGEER_3D_Gaussian_Rendering_Made_Exact_and_Efficient_for_Generic_Cameras.md", "core_operator": "将光线-粒子关联从图像空间或场景级BVH提升至相机子视锥（CSF）与粒子包围视锥（PBF）之间的精确视锥级关联，并推导出闭合形式的PBF解析解，从而在保持投影精确性的同时实现高效GPU并行化。", "datasets": ["ScanNet++", "MipNeRF360"], "method_groups": ["Vision / Multimodal / 3D", "Systems / Efficiency / Compression"], "methods": ["3DGEER"], "paper_link": "https://openreview.net/forum?id=4voMNlRWI7", "pdf_ref": "obsidian-vault/paperPDFs/ICLR_2026/3DGEER_3D_Gaussian_Rendering_Made_Exact_and_Efficient_for_Generic_Cameras.pdf", "primary_logic": "通过将每个3D高斯映射到各向同性的规范坐标系，光线-高斯密度积分可简化为闭合形式的马氏距离指数函数，该形式等价于先前工作中的“最大响应”启发式，但具有严格的投影精确性；同时，在角度域（θ, φ）中定义PBF，使得关联计算与相机模型无关，且可通过二次方程解析求解。", "project_link": "", "source": "analysis", "tags": ["topic/vision_multimodal_applications", "topic/vision_multimodal_applications/3d_rendering_reconstruction"], "title": "3DGEER: 3D Gaussian Rendering Made Exact and Efficient for Generic Cameras", "topics": ["Vision / Multimodal / Applications"], "venue": "ICLR", "year": 2026}
{"analysis_path": "obsidian-vault/analysis/ICLR_2026/Unified_Diffusion_VLA_Vision-Language-Action_Model_via_Joint_Discrete_Denosing_Diffusion_Process.md", "core_operator": "联合离散去噪扩散过程（JD3P）：将未来图像和动作 tokens 在同一个离散扩散轨迹中同步去噪，每一步动作 tokens 因果地关注图像 tokens，通过迭代精炼实现从视觉观察到动作的渐进式映射。", "datasets": ["CALVIN ABCD→D", "LIBERO", "SimplerEnv-WidowX", "JD3P Decoding Efficiency"], "method_groups": ["Vision / Multimodal / 3D", "Agent / RL / Planning"], "methods": ["UD-VLA (Unified Diffusion VLA)"], "paper_link": "https://openreview.net/forum?id=UvQOcw2oCD", "pdf_ref": "obsidian-vault/paperPDFs/ICLR_2026/Unified_Diffusion_VLA_Vision-Language-Action_Model_via_Joint_Discrete_Denosing_Diffusion_Process.pdf", "primary_logic": "同步联合去噪使得动作预测在持续、充分的未来视觉引导下由粗到精地演化，将抽象的动作推理转化为以视觉预测为条件的逆运动学问题，从而在统一的扩散轨迹中实现理解、生成和执行的深度协同。", "project_link": "", "source": "analysis", "tags": ["topic/vision_multimodal_applications", "topic/vision_multimodal_applications/robotics"], "title": "Unified Diffusion VLA: Vision-Language-Action Model via Joint Discrete Denosing Diffusion Process", "topics": ["Vision / Multimodal / Applications"], "venue": "ICLR", "year": 2026}
{"analysis_path": "obsidian-vault/analysis/ICLR_2026/In-the-Flow_Agentic_System_Optimization_for_Effective_Planning_and_Tool_Use.md", "core_operator": "Flow-GRPO 将轨迹级最终奖励广播至每个推理步骤，把多轮强化学习转化为一系列可处理的单步更新，结合组归一化优势实现稳定的在线信用分配，从而在智能体流程中直接优化规划器。", "datasets": ["Search-intensive avg.", "Agentic", "Math Reasoning avg.", "Scientific Reasoning avg."], "method_groups": ["Agent / RL / Planning", "Optimization / Theory"], "methods": ["AGENTFLOW"], "paper_link": "https://openreview.net/forum?id=Mf5AleTUVK", "pdf_ref": "obsidian-vault/paperPDFs/ICLR_2026/In-the-Flow_Agentic_System_Optimization_for_Effective_Planning_and_Tool_Use.pdf", "primary_logic": "通过将多轮交互分解为共享全局成功信号的独立单步优化，配合组归一化降低方差，使智能体系统能够在仅依靠稀疏最终奖励的情况下，高效学习长程规划与工具协调策略。", "project_link": "", "source": "analysis", "tags": ["topic/reinforcement_learning_planning_agents", "topic/reinforcement_learning_planning_agents/multi_agent"], "title": "In-the-Flow Agentic System Optimization for Effective Planning and Tool Use", "topics": ["Reinforcement Learning / Planning / Agents"], "venue": "ICLR", "year": 2026}
